data.description: Experience the charm of a 1920's Craftsman, beautifully renovated to blend timeless elegance with modern comforts. This corner lot treasure features pristine original hardwood floors, trim, and doors, complemented by a covered front porch and large backyard. Inside, discover a modernized kitchen and redesigned bathrooms that retain the home's classic appeal. Two master suites offer luxurious living, alongside practical additions like a pantry and dedicated laundry. The home boasts substantial updates: a newer roof, updated central heating and air, enhanced insulation, modern windows, and a completely replaced sewer line. Outside, the gravel circle drive and porch railings enhance the home's curb appeal. Convenience is key with a closet organization system, a tankless water heater, and a master bath complete with fresh plumbing. New stove and dishwasher stay, as well as the refrigerator, ensuring the home is move-in-ready. Welcome home to your upgraded Craftsman, where historic allure meets contemporary sophistication.
